# Pixel Art: Cyberpunk City

**What:** A 64x64 pixel art depiction of a futuristic cyberpunk cityscape at night.

**Why:** I chose this theme to capture the vibrant, tech-forward spirit of the FreelanceFlow project—representing how freelancers and clients connect in a modern, digital world full of possibilities. The neon palette and urban skyline evoke creativity, ambition, and the energy of building something new.

**File:** `cyberpunk_city.png` (64x64 pixels, PNG format)